data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in Pine Ridge North III, an all-age community that offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience! This adorable ground floor condo features 2 bedrooms and 2 baths, presenting an ideal living space for all.Step into a meticulously cared-for residence, immaculately clean and ready for you to call it home. The upgraded kitchen is a culinary delight, boasting white cabinets, granite countertops, ample cabinetry, and sleek stainless steel appliances. Bathrooms are beautifully upgraded, adding a touch of elegance to your daily routine.Gorgeous laminate flooring flows seamlessly throughout, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The master bedroom is generously sized, complete with an en suite bath and a walk-in closet, providing a perfect retreat after a long day. Accordian shutters and cable included.
As part of the all-age community, residents enjoy access to fantastic amenities, including a refreshing pool, tennis courts, a picnic area, and a playground for family fun. Conveniently located, this community offers plenty of nearby shopping options and an easy commute to major highways, ensuring that everything you need is just within reach.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming condo your own! Embrace the comfort and convenience Pine Ridge III has to offer.
